author: Caitlin O'Kane
title: Baby of firefighter dies from COVID-19, family says
description: Her father, Jerel, called her "Warrior Princess," for her fighting spirit against the horrible COVID-19 virus.
content: The 5-month-old baby of a New York City firefighter has died of coronavirus complications, according to Jose A Prosper, president of the FDNY Hispanic Society. Jay-Natalie La Santa was the daughter of the FDNY Hispanic Society's newest member, Jerel La Santa,… [+2415 chars]
